=80=9D The report explains that =E2=80=9Coil stocks dramatically underperfo=
rmed the market=E2=80=9D because of concerns about the =E2=80=9CEnd of the =
Oil Age.=E2=80=9D These demands were not hidden from the public or governme=
nt authorities. Major news organizations covered them.=C2=A0Mr. Sheffield r=
egularly discussed his views on Pioneer=E2=80=99s capital framework given s=
hareholder interest in it.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Aga=
in! If you had asked Fidelity, TIAA, Capital and BlackRock =E2=80=9Cthinkin=
g only from your perspective as shareholders=C2=A0<em>of Pioneer</em>, igno=
ring everything else, should Pioneer drill more oil or return cash,=E2=80=
