<div id=3D"footnote-1" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[1] These numbers are slightly fake for ease o=
f use. More realistically, US SRT trades seem to <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35693829.259299/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY2Fkd2FsYWRl=
ci5jb20vZnVuZC1maW5hbmNlLWZyaWRheS9pbmRleC5waHA_bmlkPTE5MiZlaWQ9MTQ2Nw/607f=
